honestly lately i've been super stressed because of high school. i mean i failed comp for the quarte cuz papa woulnd't accept my research paper.. yeah not happy but then i got a D in APES cuz i copied off of mike n jim. we aren't too smart but whatever.. school sucks and im soo happy this week was over because it was stress times 10 for this lil asian. but this weekend was pretty tight other then the fact i've had to wake up early saturday and sunday for work. that really sucks i barely got n e sleeep at all so since its sunday i'm gonna sleep til i have to go to hollister for our staff meeting. oh yeah i got my job back at hollister, cuz i go there and my old boss, Mark, he was like my favorite person there, he was like u have a paycheck still here from when u worked. i was shocked but definatly excited since it was a 77$ paycheck. i was like H yes. Then mark asked me to come back and work for him and that i could just fill out an application and just come to orientation which was this morning. and i got payed to go to orientation so thats sweet. hollister is becomin a lot more organized under mark's eye since the other managers left.. [thank goodness]. but yeah. sooo
Friday: i had dance camp early in the mornin YIKES and i was soo dead. the lil kids were adorable tho. haha soo cute. then i went to the mall with sarah to get my sisters stuff from hollister and i got my job back. then sarah, lee and i went to the game. then hung out at my house afterwards with fox. saturday: i woke up early to work. i had to go ref the lil girls. then i left to go with mindy and john [her friend] to go get chipotle and then go get our hair done. we met my brother and some girl up there. i hope this girl wasn't tryin to date my brother. since she didn't say one word to me. haha. n e ways.. i got my hair dyed more red but u can't see it really. it looks more tinted red but i wanted something more durastic. but whatever its kewl. i just can't wait til summer so i can highlight it lighter. then i go home and go out to panera with jayne, katelyn and schmid it was pretty kewl i like food.. u no..then came home cleaned, and went to pick up the SIBS for and US nite. 
now i gotta take fox home. shes been here like every nite this weekend, but right now i can't take her home cuz she insists on watchin bambi.. shes a weirdo. and if u guys saw that constipated away messege she put up on my screen name. IT WAS HER.. shes a freak..
UPDATE::: WHO WANTS TWO TURTLES?!?!?! they are stinkin up my room tooo much! they need a better home. 

leave me a cool messege :D
-corb

people kill me sometimes. of course i get bashed on a lot by ppl. im really used to it by now.. people dont know me soo i of course am just like. get a life.
but as for my friend don, i feel he gets bashed a ton, even by me, just cuz we know eachothers flaws and we know what we dislike about eachother. i love how people that dont know him can just put him out there like nothing. IF u guyz honestly knew bout DON and what he does for people u'd really like him. HE knows he's arrogant, and im proud of him being able to say that but honestly..u guyz dont even know how hard that is to say for him. but its like.. pick on someone else not him. i mean he talks about his faith, but i mean other ppl who have totally different religions or feelings talk about it too. whats the difference..

ceramics is prolly one of the easiest classes to slack in, so of course i slack even more then expected. but yet i go there and sit there, dont do much, dont make much, just talk to the kewl kids around me.. p.s. they are all pretty sweet. one in particular is one of the sweetest ever..
the cool group in ceramics haha which i think is the cool group, sits outside the actual ceramics room, u no.. to talk about the teacher. ha j/k. n e ways.. we have the usual bunch me, bill and dave then marylynn made her way out there to come hang, and last but not least.. nicole made her way out there, to make the table complete. she never really talked much, but she seemed quiet and kept to herself. all i knew was she had beautiful blue eyes and really cool dark hair.. little did i know she would be readin my crazy journals entries.
so one day over break, i of course have one of these weird journals, talking about change, and what it has been doin in my life, with my friends, family n wut not. i of course have been very emotionally upset around that time too. but do i keep my head down? no no no, because the next day i pop in to see i have 2 comments, from one lovely girl who actually took time to read my journal, and better yet leave a comment showin her feelings and gratitude! i dont even get that from my closesets friends. im sure u all can guess what blue eyed beauty this was..
what i've realized is that Nicole, mite not be the person i go and spill my heart out to, but thats ok, we aren't that close, but to just know that someone cares, someone that u dont know too well. thats a great feeling and i applaud her each chance i can to let ppl no that you have a lot of effect on people, nice gestuers go a long way.
Nicole i believe has had it a lil rough down the road. i mean shes got a cool family im sure, maybe some problems here and there, but who doesnt? Nicole takes care of her brothers and sisters all the time. she is like a mom. i applaud her because i definatly dont know what that is like, being the only child, and seein her just amazes me. she also is heavily in love with a young boy named Greg, sometimes u can't help but laugh because shes soo cute about him, and then i remember what its like to be in love and you can't do much but smile. this girl always amazes me and even though we aren't super close, the respect i have for her is well deserved. what a beautiful person.

so the last couple weeks have been soo emotional for me. i can't even believe how things change, how people change, how they said one thing and now are for another thing. i've found myself being changed also.
I love the people i hang out with and i love all my friends but i just need to go to college. i need to meet new people i need to stop being with the ppl that remind me of certain things, certain places in my life. i need a find someone new to love to get over my last one if i can. i need a lot of things right now but i just have to be patience. love is patient, something i have to work on.
i still hang on to someone i dont know. i dont know if the person i fell in love with still exisits..all i no is that there is love there that i wish wasn't. then i could get over all my hurt and all my pain and he could go on with out me.. happy and then i could be happy. life would be swell..i guess GOd is teaching me a huge lesson here. it just sucks beyond n e thing. i can't even cry because it sucks soo bad. Even though im a christian no where does it say you'll always be happy. I mean you'll have your joy from the holy spirit n wut not. but things still happen in your life. and obviously they happen for a reason. i just need sit back and let whatever happen happen, even tho it will prolly tear me apart i must be strong.
i think im gonna be tramatized by love the rest of my life..  im scared of boys.. they hurt u.
Today i went to my box, i have a box dedciated to my 2 year relationship. i had a notebook, that clearly was just full of entrys bout him.. yup threw that away... those things just remind me and sometimes its not the best. 
other then my wonderful weeks um.. its snowin relaly hard today and i hope we dont have school tomorrow. cuz i dislike school like woah. and umm.. i realllllllllly wanna go to 707 so i think im gonna drive out there. which mite be a lil crazy but honestly i dont care. i need some praise and worship time.

as he sits there with his eyes dripping, she starts to cry. She has never seen him that way. He said " no on will love you more than me, you wont find anyone better" she sat and cried, she knew she hurt him. She believed his words, they were soothing, they made her feel exactly how she wanted to feel... loved..he filled a void of pain. a void that can no longer be filled by him. 
she was dumb enough to believe his words..but now the words that were once soothing, hurt, because knowing that people change, and not always for the best. She was stupid enough to believe him. he will never understand the hurt he has always put on her...
